Get property values

Returns vector of property values for specified molecular database and property name

get_prop_vec(moldbase, propname)

Arguments

moldbase

Molecular database
propname

Property name

Value

Vector of property values

Examples

data("alkans74")
get_prop_vec(alkans74.mdb, "bp")
